name: The Magician Tarot Card
description:
The Magician brings you the tools, resources and energy you need to make your dreams come true.Everything you need right now is at your fingertips. Now is the perfect time to move forward on an idea that you recently conceived. The seed of potential has sprouted, and you are being called to take action and bring your intention to fruition. The skills, knowledge and capabilities you have gathered along your life path have led you to where you are now, and whether or not you know it, you are ready to turn your ideas into reality.
Created by Brian from Chicago @thebrau
